'''Will Conrad''' is a comic book artist. He pencilled "[[The Way of the Warrior (comic story)|The Way of the Warrior]]" in ''[[Star Wars Tales 18]]''. Conrad has also drawn the ''Serenity'' comics [[W:c:firefly:Serenity: Those Left Behind|''Those Left Behind'']], [[W:c:firefly:Serenity: Better Days|''Better Days'']], and [[W:c:firefly:Serenity: The Other Half|''The Other Half'']].

